stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created
    Created --> Discovering
    Discovering --> Scanning: eligible volume
    Scanning --> Aggregating: enumeration ended
    Aggregating --> Classifying
    Classifying --> Persisting
    Persisting --> Completed
    Discovering --> Failed: unsupported or fatal discovery error
    Discovering --> DriveRemoved
    Scanning --> Cancelled: before useful aggregate
    Scanning --> Partial: cancelled with results or isolated errors
    Scanning --> DriveRemoved
    Scanning --> Failed: non-isolatable fault
    Aggregating --> Partial: incomplete observation
    Classifying --> Partial: recoverable rule failure
    Persisting --> Partial: snapshot unavailable, result retained
    Completed --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
    Partial --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
    DriveRemoved --> [*]
